  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<h1 class=\"size-48 is-title1-48 is-title-bold\">~宇宙模擬~</h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<div class=\"edit\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"></span><span style=\"font-size:20px;\">物奧/亞太物奧雙金，目前公費留學於天文物理的聖地，執美國光學、天體物理牛耳的 University of Arizona天文所博士班研究的林昱嘉老師製作模擬，與大家分享！<br />\n<br />\n影片從近乎均勻的原始宇宙出發，模擬數億甚至數十億光年的大尺度結構（Large-scale structure)如何在宇宙中形成，讓我們一起跨越時空體驗宇宙之美。<br />\n<br />\n※星期日(10/9)上午10:30 ~12:00，專訪林昱嘉老師，如何成為物理高手、如何準備物理競賽，歡迎參加！</span></div>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1142031846749499/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/1142031846749499/</a></span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column full\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-16by9\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/sYhtagJwGU0?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
